<p>LG dryer motor replacement costs <strong>$380–480 total</strong> in Los Angeles, Orange County, and Ventura County — OEM motor, belt and idler pulley replacement at the same visit, blower wheel inspection, full test cycle, and 1-year warranty. The $65 diagnostic fee is waived when you approve the repair. This is the most expensive mechanical repair we do on LG dryers. We're honest about when it makes sense — this page covers both the repair and when we'd tell you not to bother.</p>
